{"tid":2371524,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有仔女嘅巴絲, 你哋嘅小朋友主要邊個照顧?搵錯人照顧, 小心仔女變小粉紅","createTime":"2021-01-19T02:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T14:28:19.000Z","uid":204929,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d1bfe6c783336eb98b10986566f0350cbf5990d1","tid":2371524,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:52:49.000Z","msg":"有時見到因為工作繁忙, 所以啲仔女會交畀小朋友嘅阿爺阿嫲照顧, <br />\n但係見到呢個現象好擔心, 因為好多老一輩都係 藍/紅, 你諗下, 畀佢哋照顧小朋友會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n如果你哋父母係黃就冇問題啦, 如果係 藍/紅嘅, 應該淨係一個人做嘢, 一個人照顧小朋友.<br />\n<br />\n喺依家黨安法之後, 照顧佢嘅人係藍/紅嘅話, 咁好難將自己嘅理念講畀小朋友.<br />\n<br />\n好似好多人都冇諗過呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 自己仔女變小粉紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 到時唔好仆街喊.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能又有人話唔生, 不過唔生嘅話香港人種族滅絕. <br />\n生嘅, 去外國生."},{"pid":"4e48c13792bf8f40b4975442f19f50ec8f417e5a","tid":2371524,"uid":41368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:54:36.000Z","msg":"咁日日返學<br />\n學校方面又可以點阻止"},{"pid":"c4bec73fcbfe4dc9f3c3fb6e6aeba1fe06acffa9","tid":2371524,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e48c13792bf8f40b4975442f19f50ec8f417e5a","tid":2371524,"uid":41368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:54:36.000Z","msg":"咁日日返學<br />\n學校方面又可以點阻止"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:55:53.000Z","msg":"唔好揀左校"},{"pid":"1e0dd1b39f635d1cb25be48b198f121904e260e7","tid":2371524,"uid":41368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c4bec73fcbfe4dc9f3c3fb6e6aeba1fe06acffa9","tid":2371524,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e48c13792bf8f40b4975442f19f50ec8f417e5a","tid":2371524,"uid":41368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:54:36.000Z","msg":"咁日日返學<br />\n學校方面又可以點阻止"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:55:53.000Z","msg":"唔好揀左校"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T02:56:47.000Z","msg":"有無例子<br 